<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('partials/head') %>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <main>
        <div class="container-custom py-10 md:py-16">
            <section class="style-shell px-6 py-8 md:px-10 md:py-12">
                <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0">
                    <div class="absolute left-[-2rem] top-10 h-44 w-44 rounded-full bg-accent-purple/12 blur-3xl"></div>
                    <div class="absolute bottom-[-3rem] right-[-1rem] h-52 w-52 rounded-full bg-gold/20 blur-3xl"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="relative z-10 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_0.9fr] lg:items-center">
                    <div>
                        <span class="style-kicker mb-6">Live workshops and community calls</span>
                        <h1 class="title font-cormorant text-5xl md:text-7xl text-accent-purple mb-4 font-medium">Vagus Nerve Live Workshop!</h1>
                        <p class="subtitle font-cormorant text-2xl md:text-3xl text-gold leading-tight">Join Us for a Transformative Experience</p>
                        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-dark-text/85 md:text-xl">
                            Join the Vagus Skool for our live vagus nerve stimulation workshops. We host regular interactive sessions to help you master these transformative techniques with guidance and community support.
                        </p>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-accent-purple md:text-xl">
                            We would love to have you join us live. Please check our community calendar below to see all upcoming workshop dates and times.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="grid gap-4">
                        <div class="style-metric">
                            <p class="section-label">Bring with you</p>
                            <p class="mt-3 text-lg text-dark-text/80">Your VNS tools, your questions, and a willingness to practice in real time.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="style-metric">
                            <p class="section-label">What to expect</p>
                            <p class="mt-3 text-lg text-dark-text/80">Live guidance, scheduled sessions, and an easier path into consistency and feedback.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <div class="mt-8 section-shell text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                <h2 class="font-cormorant text-3xl md:text-4xl text-accent-purple font-medium mb-4">Stay Connected</h2>
                <p class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-lg text-dark-text/90 mb-8">
                    All live events, workshops, and community calls are listed on our official Skool calendar. Bring your VNS tools and your questions.
                </p>

                <button id="calendar-button" class="golden-button w-full md:w-auto">
                    View Workshop Calendar
                </button>
                <p class="mt-4 text-accent-purple text-sm md:text-base opacity-90">Join our growing community and start your healing journey today.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

    <script>
        // Calendar button click handler
        document.getElementById('calendar-button').addEventListener('click', () => {
            window.location.href = 'https://www.skool.com/vagus/calendar';
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
